{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"z2-quiz-3","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"专题集训","title":"专题集训二 第3题","difficulty":4,"tags":["有理数","规律"],"content":"已知 $a$ 为不等于 1 的有理数，我们把 $\\frac{1}{1-a}$ 叫做 $a$ 的差倒数。\n\n（1）$-\\frac{1}{2}$ 的差倒数是______；\n（2）若 $a_1 = -3$，$a_2$ 是 $a_1$ 的差倒数，$a_3$ 是 $a_2$ 的差倒数...以此类推，则 $a_3 = $______；\n（3）按照以上规律，求 $a_1 + a_2 + ... + a_{2025}$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"(1) $\\frac{1}{1-(-\\frac{1}{2})} = \\frac{1}{\\frac{3}{2}} = \\frac{2}{3}$\n\n(2) $a_2 = \\frac{1}{1-(-3)} = \\frac{1}{4}$\n$a_3 = \\frac{1}{1-\\frac{1}{4}} = \\frac{4}{3}$","formula":""}]},"id":"z2-quiz-3"},"__N_SSG":true}